reviewText: Absolutely love this movie so much, I got like 3 copies and got half of Dallas watching it....two thumbs up....Peace, Love, and Blessings

I got this movie from Redbox just trying to find something to waste a couple hours. I had never heard of this movie and was just giving it a try. I was shocked because after watching it I can say it is a certified classic. You know its not a big box office production but its not bottom barrel low budget either. It has a couple of nice plot twists, good cinematography and good acting. I will buy this movie because it is good enough to watch over and over. I highly reccommend this movie. The bad review just didn't give it a chance. It's worth watching.
This was a really good movie and it had some twists in there.  Overall, I reccommend this movie to people.  I really enjoyed this movie!
